---
---
<section class="section interests-section" id="interests">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-center reveal">
      <div class="glow-badge">AREAS OF EXCELLENCE</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Pioneering the <span class="text-gradient">Future of Neuro-care</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Four pillars of innovation, clinical excellence, and systemic transformation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="interests-grid">
      <!-- Card 1: Neuro Modulation -->
      <div class="interest-box reveal">
        <div class="interest-header">
           <div class="interest-icon">🧠</div>
           <h3 class="interest-name">Neuro Modulation & Functional Surgery</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="interest-p">
          Stereotactic & Functional Neurosurgery, Stereotactic Radiosurgery (SRS), and specialized Neuro Rehabilitation protocols. Circuit-based ablation surgeries, Intrathecal Baclofen Pumps, and Deep Brain Stimulation (DBS).
        </p>
        <div class="institute-badge">
           <strong>JIOMSN</strong>
           <p>Movement Disorders & Neurosurgery — dedicated to Parkinson's, Tremors, Dystonia & Intractable Pain. Pioneering RF and ablative surgeries in India.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="tag">DBS</span>
          <span class="tag">ITB Pump</span>
          <span class="tag">VO Thalamotomy</span>
          <span class="tag">SRS</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Rehabilitation Technology -->
      <div class="interest-box premium-box reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="glow-blob"></div>
        <div class="interest-header">
           <div class="interest-icon">⚙️</div>
           <h3 class="interest-name">Rehabilitation Technology — Made in India</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="interest-p">
          Under <strong>Newro Kaaya Innovative Solutions</strong>, Dr. Sharan's team has built 5 indigenous rehab devices — high-quality, affordable neurotechnology tailored to real patient needs and Indian financial realities.
        </p>
        <ul class="device-list">
          <li>
            <div class="check">✓</div>
            <span><strong>Holosuit:</strong> Next-gen rehabilitation tech.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="check">✓</div>
            <span><strong>WALK-FREE:</strong> Motorized body-weight support system.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="check">✓</div>
            <span><strong>Balance Pro:</strong> Low-cost Bluetooth assessment.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="check">✓</div>
            <span><strong>Upper Limb Unweighing:</strong> Stroke rehab system.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="made-in-badge">🇮🇳 Athmanirbhar Bharat · Made for the World</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: newro LOGICS -->
      <div class="interest-box software-box reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="interest-header">
           <div class="interest-icon">💻</div>
           <h3 class="interest-name">newro LOGICS — Clinic-to-Commerce SaaS</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="interest-p">
          A proprietary platform that <strong>objectifies subjective clinical insights</strong> in neurorehabilitation — the first solution of its kind. Objectively measure clinical function, optimize outcomes, and manage both clinical and business aspects seamlessly.
        </p>
        <div class="award-ribbon">
          <span class="award-icon">🏆</span>
          <div>
            <strong>National Winner — NBEC 2022</strong>
            <p>Grand Finale · C-CAMP, Govt. of India · 3,000+ competitors</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="interest-p mt-3">
          Powered by the <strong>CAREPa-Re™ Framework</strong> — turning complex neurobehavioral profiles into actionable clinical data.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4: Academic Reform -->
      <div class="interest-box reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="interest-header">
           <div class="interest-icon">🎓</div>
           <h3 class="interest-name">Academic Reform & Education</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="interest-p">
          In 2012, Dr. Sharan discovered Karnataka had only one college offering Occupational Therapy. He directly approached the Vice-Chancellor of RGUHS, assembled a curriculum team, and pushed it through multiple approval levels — changing the landscape of neurorehabilitation education across the state.
        </p>
        <div class="edu-timeline">
          <div class="edu-item">
            <span class="edu-year">2012</span>
            <span class="edu-text">BOT & MOT programs introduced under RGUHS, Karnataka</span>
          </div>
          <div class="edu-item">
            <span class="edu-year">2025</span>
            <span class="edu-text">New partnership with <strong>Jain University</strong> — launching BOT/MOT programs</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="institute-badge mt-3">
          <strong>LMS Platform</strong>
          <p>A custom Learning Management System to standardize neurorehabilitation education nationally.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .interests-section {
    background-color: var(--bg-slate);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .section-center {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .glow-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 20px;
    background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1);
    color: var(--primary-color);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .section-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .interests-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .interest-box {
    background: white;
    padding: 48px 36px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    position: relative;
    transition: var(--transition-smooth);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .interest-box:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-premium);
  }

  .interest-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .interest-icon {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    background: var(--bg-slate);
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 18px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .interest-name {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--text-main);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .interest-p {
    font-size: 0.97rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .mt-3 { margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 0 !important; }

  .institute-badge {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.05) 0%, rgba(126, 34, 206, 0.05) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  .institute-badge strong {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    font-size: 1rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .institute-badge p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .tag-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .tag {
    padding: 4px 12px;
    background: var(--bg-slate);
    border: 1px solid rgba(79,70,229,0.15);
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }

  /* Premium dark card */
  .premium-box {
    background: #0f172a;
    color: white;
  }

  .premium-box .interest-name { color: white; }
  .premium-box .interest-p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65); }
  .premium-box .interest-p strong { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); }

  .glow-blob {
    position: absolute;
    top: -50px;
    right: -50px;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--primary-color) 0%, transparent 70%);
    opacity: 0.2;
    filter: blur(40px);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .device-list {
    margin-top: 20px;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .device-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .check {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    background: var(--accent-color);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: bold;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .device-list span { font-size: 0.92rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); line-height: 1.5; }
  .device-list strong { color: var(--accent-color); }

  .made-in-badge {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    text-align: center;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  /* Software card */
  .software-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8faff 0%, #f0f4ff 100%);
    border-color: rgba(79,70,229,0.1);
  }

  .software-box .interest-icon { background: rgba(79,70,229,0.08); }

  .award-ribbon {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(79,70,229,0.08) 0%, rgba(126,34,206,0.08) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(79,70,229,0.15);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 18px;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  .award-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .award-ribbon strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-main);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .award-ribbon p {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* Education card */
  .edu-timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  .edu-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .edu-year {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    background: rgba(79,70,229,0.08);
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .edu-text {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .edu-text strong { color: var(--text-main); }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .interest-name { font-size: 1.25rem; }
    .interest-box { padding: 36px 28px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .interests-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .section-title { font-size: 2.5rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-title { font-size: 2rem; }
    .interest-box { padding: 28px 22px; }
    .interest-name { font-size: 1.15rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .section-title { font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .interest-icon { width: 52px; height: 52px; font-size: 1.8rem; }
  }
</style>
